---
const categories = ['Guitarras', 'Amplificadores', 'Pedais', 'Acessórios', 'Guias de Compra', 'Dicas para Iniciantes'];

const links = [
  { href: '/blog', label: 'Todas as Análises' },
  { href: '/about', label: 'Sobre Nós' },
  { href: '/contact', label: 'Contato' },
  { href: '/rss.xml', label: 'Feed RSS' },
];

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-border mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-10 mb-12">
      <!-- Coluna da marca -->
      <div class="sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-xl mb-4">
          <span class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-brand rounded-lg text-white" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round">
              <path d="M9 18V5l12-2v13" />
              <circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3" />
              <circle cx="18" cy="16" r="3" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          Sonar<span class="text-brand">Musical</span>
        </a>
        <p class="text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
          Análises honestas, guias de compra e dicas para guitarristas de todos os níveis. Te ajudamos a encontrar o equipamento certo sem enrolação.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links rápidos -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted mb-4">Links Rápidos</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
          {links.map(({ href, label }) => (
            <li>
              <a href={href} class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">
                {label}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Categorias -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-muted mb-4">Categorias</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
          {categories.map((cat) => (
            <li>
              <a
                href={`/blog?categoria=${encodeURIComponent(cat)}`}
                class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors"
              >
                {cat}
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Rodapé inferior -->
    <div class="border-t border-border pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-muted">
      <p>&copy; {year} Sonar Musical. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
      <p>Feito com <a href="https://astro.build" class="hover:text-white transition-colors underline underline-offset-2" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Astro</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
